{"tid":1517926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛主席：必須在廣闊的戰場上進行高度的運動戰","createTime":"2019-08-30T05:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T12:41:51.000Z","uid":272805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d37aa25682921a41432f1d4b462c72f4db52f743","tid":1517926,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"必須在廣闊的戰場上進行高度的運動戰，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">迅速地前進和迅速地後退，迅速地集中和迅速地分散</span></span></strong>。 這就是大規模的運動戰，而不是深溝高壘、層層設防、專靠防禦工事的陣地戰"},{"pid":"ccadd1b8eb4d1b95a510adfee83f98395009dfbb","tid":1517926,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a916d9897d6affc34e14a5baeb0a6763b1de8b","tid":1517926,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:29:47.000Z","msg":"感謝毛主席的教導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654e80d60be6f38df5d775a740c0aafd4ca0a3af","tid":1517926,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:31:25.000Z","msg":"香港街道一d 都唔廣闊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87b508be9d15457b4e63b6b89b8b065bcfeb560","tid":1517926,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:31:32.000Z","msg":"並不是說要放棄一切重要的軍事地點，對於這些地點，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">衹要有利，就應配置陣地戰</span></span>。"},{"pid":"8fbba64c0b7b4d2d86b401113d755150208fdee7","tid":1517926,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:32:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉換全局的戰略方針，必然要是運動戰。 陣地戰雖也必需，但是屬於輔助性質的第二種的方針</span></span>"},{"pid":"7b1f116e047b889857aab83e4833752e0ab9332f","tid":1517926,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:34:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他們的戰爭機構很笨重，行動很慢，效力有限。 如果我們集中兵力在一個狹小的陣地上作消耗戰的抵抗，將使我軍失掉地理上的和經濟組織上的有利條件，犯阿比西尼亞的錯誤。</span></span>"},{"pid":"f1b8280b3f626929a22b1e6c558a46e9a21ca734","tid":1517926,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:35:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們要避免一切大的決戰，要先用運動戰逐漸地破壞敵人軍隊的精神和戰鬥力。</span></span>"},{"pid":"d63fe1294f651da72f46a73e19b66ac698905000","tid":1517926,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"除了調動有訓練的軍隊進行運動戰之外，還要在農民中組織很多的遊擊隊。 須知東三省的抗日義勇軍，僅僅是表示了全國農民所能動員抗戰的潛伏力量的一小部分。"},{"pid":"b25984cd44b2ddbc163d8a7bdde1fec80b409d60","tid":1517926,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:44:56.000Z","msg":"中國農民有很大的潛伏力，衹要組織和指揮得當，能使日本軍隊一天忙碌二十四小時，使之疲於奔命。 必須記住這個戰爭是在中國打的，這就是說，日軍要完全被敵對的中國人所包圍﹔日軍要被迫運來他們所需的軍用品，而且要自己看守﹔他們要用重兵去保護 交通線，時時謹防襲擊"},{"pid":"921ebe98374a62267c07a3ea9809d0fee7675d55","tid":1517926,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:41:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}